description: Aaron Steindler  added  25 new photos  — with  Stephanie Lyn  and  3 others  at  Havasupai Falls in Supai, Arizona (Supai Indian Reservation) . Last night I,  Daniel Oliver ,  Stephanie Lyn ,  Dea Applegate , and  Ginger Hike  returned from Havasupai, an Indian reservation deep into the Grand Canyon.  For those of you who don't know, it is known for its deep, turquoise water, and it is very difficult to obtain a permit to go here due to the high demand from people all over the world wanting to come here.  Believe it or not, this is in Arizona, yet it looks like a tropical paradise.  Here are some of the pictures that I took
